---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'April 24, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for B2B Solutions — how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <Header />

  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 to-blue-700 text-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-blue prose-lg max-w-none
        prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:text-gray-900
        prose-p:text-gray-600 prose-p:leading-relaxed
        prose-a:text-blue-700 prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline
        prose-strong:text-gray-900
        prose-ul:text-gray-600 prose-li:leading-relaxed
        prose-h2:text-2xl prose-h2:mt-10 prose-h2:mb-4
        prose-h3:text-lg prose-h3:mt-6 prose-h3:mb-2">

        <p>B2B Solutions ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or interact with us. Please read this policy carefully.</p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
        <p>We collect information you voluntarily provide when you:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fill out a contact or inquiry form</li>
          <li>Schedule a consultation through our booking system</li>
          <li>Communicate with us by email, phone, or text message</li>
          <li>Engage us for services</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This may include your name, business name, email address, phone number, and any details you share about your business needs.</p>

        <h3>Information Collected Automatically</h3>
        <p>When you visit our website, we may automatically collect certain technical information, including your IP address, browser type, pages visited, and time spent on pages. This information is used to improve our website and is not linked to your personal identity.</p>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide the services you request</li>
          <li>Schedule and manage consultations and appointments</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about your account or services</li>
          <li>Send you relevant business updates, tips, and marketing communications (with your consent)</li>
          <li>Improve our website and services</li>
          <li>Comply with applicable laws and regulations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. SMS / Text Message Communications</h2>

        <h3>SMS Marketing and Client Communications</h3>
        <p>B2B Solutions uses SMS (text messaging) for both client service communications and marketing purposes. By providing your mobile phone number and opting in, you consent to receive text messages from us.</p>

        <h3>Types of SMS Messages</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Service messages:</strong> Appointment reminders, follow-ups, and communications related to your engagement with B2B Solutions.</li>
          <li><strong>Marketing messages:</strong> Promotions, business tips, service announcements, and other marketing content.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Opt-In</h3>
        <p>By submitting your phone number through our contact form, booking system, or any other point of collection and expressly agreeing to receive text messages, you consent to receive SMS communications from B2B Solutions. Message frequency may vary.</p>

        <h3>Opt-Out</h3>
        <p>You may opt out of SMS communications at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any message you receive from us. After opting out, you will receive one final confirmation message and no further texts will be sent. To re-subscribe, reply <strong>START</strong>.</p>

        <h3>Help</h3>
        <p>Reply <strong>HELP</strong> to any SMS message for assistance, or contact us directly at <a href="mailto:info@b2bsolutions.biz">info@b2bsolutions.biz</a>.</p>

        <h3>Message and Data Rates</h3>
        <p>Message and data rates may apply depending on your mobile carrier and plan. B2B Solutions is not responsible for any charges incurred from your carrier.</p>

        <h3>Carrier Disclaimer</h3>
        <p>Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages.</p>

        <h2>4. How We Share Your Information</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information only in the following limited circumstances:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> Trusted third-party vendors who assist us in operating our website and delivering services (such as scheduling platforms and CRM software), subject to confidentiality agreements.</li>
          <li><strong>Legal requirements:</strong> If required by law, court order, or governmental authority.</li>
          <li><strong>Business protection:</strong> To protect the rights, property, or safety of B2B Solutions, our clients, or others.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to provide our services and comply with our legal obligations. If you would like us to delete your information, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@b2bsolutions.biz">info@b2bsolutions.biz</a>.</p>

        <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

        <h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites (such as Zoho Forms and Zoho Bookings). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites and encourage you to review their privacy policies.</p>

        <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our services are not directed to individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

        <h2>9. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal information, including the right to access, correct, or delete data we hold about you. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@b2bsolutions.biz">info@b2bsolutions.biz</a>.</p>

        <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. Your continued use of our website or services after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the revised policy.</p>

        <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@b2bsolutions.biz">info@b2bsolutions.biz</a></li>
          <li><strong>Phone (West Coast):</strong> <a href="tel:3605292672">360-529-2672</a></li>
          <li><strong>Phone (Midwest):</strong> <a href="tel:3194510501">319-451-0501</a></li>
          <li><strong>Locations:</strong> Rochester, WA &amp; Cedar Rapids, IA</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
